# ------------------------------
# Terraform
# ------------------------------
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl.backup
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.*
**/crash.log
**/crash.*.log

# CLI overrides (rarely committed)
**/override.tf
**/override.tf.json
**/*_override.tf
**/*_override.tf.json

# Variables files (often contain secrets)
**/*.tfvars
**/*.tfvars.json
**/*.auto.tfvars
**/*.auto.tfvars.json
!**/*.tfvars.example
!**/*.auto.tfvars.example

# Local plan output
**/*.tfplan

# ------------------------------
# Helm
# ------------------------------
# Packaged charts
**/*.tgz

# Dependency builds
**/charts/

# Helm lockfile is often reproducible; ignore if you don't want it committed
**/Chart.lock
